&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;&amp;lt;span class=&amp;#34;line&amp;#34;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;span class=&amp;#34;cl&amp;#34;&amp;gt; &amp;amp;#34;Category 2&amp;amp;#34;
